    <id>https://www.harimenon.com/blog/2016/11/06/the-desert</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>The sun is blazing<br />
There's no water<br />
There's almost no food<br />
There's only animals<br /></p>

<p>I love the desert<br />
Be careful<br />
Because there's cactus<br />
It has thorns<br /></p>

<br />


<p> - Maya Haridas</p>

<blockquote><p>The very first poem by (5.5 yo) Maya - 11/05/2016
🌵 🐫</p></blockquote>
